What this adds conceptually

This turns your system from:
	•	preference learning only

into:
	•	preference learning + governed aggregation

So now you can answer questions like:
	•	which users should count more for a given decision
	•	how expert input should mix with crowd input
	•	how to penalize outputs that violate system invariants
	•	how to personalize without losing shared coherence

Clean next move

After this, the strongest upgrade is a reputation ledger:
	•	source scores update over time
	•	predictive accuracy gets measured against later outcomes
	•	manipulation risk increases when behavior looks adversarial
	•	governance weights can shift by domain

That would make it feel alive.